Apple-Shop
---------------
Backend Development ---->

1. Create Migration File For Database
   pa make:migration create_users
   pa make:migration create_customer_profiles
   pa make:migration create_categories
   pa make:migration create_brands
   pa make:migration create_products
   pa make:migration create_product_reviews
   pa make:migration create_product_details
   pa make:migration create_product_sliders
   pa make:migration create_product_wishes
   pa make:migration create_product_carts
   pa make:migration create_sslcommerz_accounts
   pa make:migration create_invoices
   pa make:migration create_invoice_products
   pa make:migration create_policies

user php artisan make:migration table_name --m

2. Create Model File For Database and add Fillable Attribute
   pa make:Model User
   pa make:Model CustomerProfile
   pa make:Model Category
   pa make:Model Brand
   pa make:Model Product
   pa make:Model ProductReview
   pa make:Model ProductDetail
   pa make:Model ProductSlider
   pa make:Model ProductWish
   pa make:Model ProductCart
   pa make:Model SslcommerzAccount
   pa make:Model Invoice
   pa make:Model InvoiceProduct
   pa make:Model Policy


3. Create Controller File
    pa make:controller UserController
    pa make:controller ProfileController
    pa make:controller BrandController
    pa make:controller CategoryController
    pa make:controller ProductController
    pa make:controller InvoiceController
    pa make:controller PolicyController

4. Build Logic inside Controller for data view
    Brand
    Category
    product
    Customer_Profile
    Invoice
    Product Invoice
    Payment

